comments: Birch (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ingles (UTA) and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick,.
Gobert (UTA) makes incidental contact with Anunoby's (TOR) leg as he gets control of the loose ball during the rebound.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes marginal contact with VanVleet's (TOR) body at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
VanVleet (TOR) releases from Ingles (UTA) at the end of his drive.
Birch (TOR) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Clarkson's (UTA) body that dislodges him.
Gobert (UTA) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Anunoby (TOR) makes incidental contact to Clarkson's (UTA) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Birch (TOR) extends an arm into Gobert (UTA) and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Bogdanovic (UTA) moves slightly into Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact to his body during the driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) gets drawn in the air and makes contact with Clarkson's (UTA) arm that affects his ability to pass.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly deflects the ball away from Clarkson (UTA) and out of bounds and possession is correctly given to Utah.
Flynn (TOR) commits a take foul on Ingles (UTA).
